00:11:36,629 --> 00:11:38,229
痛い痛い痛い！
Ow ow ow ow!

165
00:11:40,529 --> 00:11:41,729
わりゃ！
Take that!

166
00:11:42,329 --> 00:11:43,729
怖い怖い怖い！
Scary, scary, scary!

167
00:11:44,229 --> 00:11:46,129
えーと、こういう時は...
U-Um, in times like these...

168
00:11:47,929 --> 00:11:49,929
ト、トリック・オア・トリート！
T-Trick or Treat!

169
00:11:50,329 --> 00:11:51,929
何もかも違うだろ！
That's wrong in every possible way!

170
00:12:01,929 --> 00:12:04,429
顔が、顔が変になってるよ！
Her face... her face is turning weird!

171
00:12:05,429 --> 00:12:06,429
フブちゃん！
Fubu-chan!

172
00:12:09,429 --> 00:12:10,429
フブちゃん！
Fubu-chan!

173
00:12:10,529 --> 00:12:12,429
出てる出てる！楽しいの素が出たな！
It's coming out! Her essence of fun is coming out!

174
00:12:12,529 --> 00:12:13,929
よいしょ！
Heave-ho!

175
00:12:20,229 --> 00:12:23,429
でも、コラプサーが出てくるってことは...
Ugh... But if the Corrupsas are appearing...

176
00:12:24,229 --> 00:12:27,529
夢落ちしてる人がいるんだ、多分。
Someone must be suffering a Dream Fall, probably.

177
00:12:31,929 --> 00:12:32,729
ミオ先輩！
Mio-senpai!

178
00:12:33,729 --> 00:12:34,629
ミオちゃん！
Mio-chan!

179
00:12:37,529 --> 00:12:39,329
ご、ごめん。うち、うち...
I-I'm sorry. I... I...

180
00:12:39,929 --> 00:12:42,329
本当は、本当は...
Actually, actually...

181
00:12:43,529 --> 00:12:46,329
ハロウィンのカボチャが怖くてだめなのー！
I'm just so terrified of Halloween pumpkins that I can't do anything!

182
00:12:50,829 --> 00:12:55,929
ちっちゃい頃、パパがハロウィンであれ被って帰ってきて...
When I was little, my dad came home for Halloween wearing one of those...

183
00:12:56,529 --> 00:12:58,229
ただいまー
I'm home!

184
00:12:57,329 --> 00:13:01,129
うち、パパがカボチャに食べられちゃったんだって思っちゃって。
And I thought a pumpkin had eaten my daddy.

185
00:13:01,229 --> 00:13:02,929
ハッピーハロウィーン！！
Happy Halloween!!

186
00:13:02,929 --> 00:13:05,429
それから、
Ever since then,

187
00:13:06,629 --> 00:13:08,429
どうしても、
no matter what,

188
00:13:09,829 --> 00:13:13,429
ハロウィンのカボチャだけは、
Halloween pumpkins are the one thing

189
00:13:13,529 --> 00:13:16,929
無理なのー！
I just can't handle!

190
00:13:41,529 --> 00:13:42,529
チェンジ！
Change!

191
00:13:44,129 --> 00:13:45,429
ガーディアン・アーム！
Guardian Arm!

192
00:13:45,929 --> 00:13:47,129
巫女神の輪（みこがみのろった）！
Mikogami no Rotta!

193
00:13:47,729 --> 00:13:50,429
キャンディー・パラソル！
Candy Parasol!

194
00:13:51,229 --> 00:13:52,429
頑張りな！
Go for it!

195
00:13:52,929 --> 00:13:54,729
スノーフレーク・セイバー！
Snowflake Saber!

196
00:13:55,129 --> 00:13:56,529
吹切丸（ふぶきりまる）！
Fubukirimaru!

197
00:13:57,229 --> 00:13:58,629
ここは任せて、ミオ。
Leave this to us, Mio.

198
00:13:59,529 --> 00:14:00,529
みんな...
Everyone...

199
00:14:04,929 --> 00:14:07,429
魔法、みんなに見せちゃうけど、いいよね？
We're going to show everyone our magic, okay?

200
00:14:09,129 --> 00:14:11,429
うん、そんなこと言ってらんないし。
Yeah, we don't have time to worry about that now.

201
00:14:12,429 --> 00:14:15,529
だよね！夢落ちした人を助ける。それが...
Right! Helping people who suffer a Dream Fall. That is...

202
00:14:16,129 --> 00:14:18,729
魔法少女、ホロウィッチ！
...Magical Girl HoloWitch!

203
00:14:21,329 --> 00:14:25,629
この手を差し伸べ、掴んで、握る。
Reach out this hand, seize, and hold tight.

204
00:14:25,929 --> 00:14:28,729
天音のホロ、魔法少女かなた！
The Holo of Amane, Magical Girl Kanata!

205
00:14:30,429 --> 00:14:33,229
みんなの願いを咲かせる祈り。
A prayer to make everyone's wishes bloom.

206
00:14:33,429 --> 00:14:36,329
みこのホロ、魔法少女みこ！
The Holo of Miko, Magical Girl Miko!

207
00:14:37,929 --> 00:14:41,129
甘い幸せ、お裾分け。
A helping of sweet happiness.

208
00:14:41,229 --> 00:14:44,129
姫森のホロ、魔法少女ルーナ！
The Holo of Himemori, Magical Girl Luna!

209
00:14:46,329 --> 00:14:49,229
きらめくお宝、ロックオン。
Sparkling treasures, locked on.

210
00:14:49,429 --> 00:14:52,429
海賊のホロ、魔法少女マリン！
The Holo of the Pirate, Magical Girl Marine!

211
00:14:54,229 --> 00:14:57,229
心躍らすトリックスター。
The heart-dancing trickster.

212
00:14:57,429 --> 00:15:00,729
狐のホロ、魔法少女フブキ！
The Holo of the Fox, Magical Girl Fubuki!

213
00:15:02,377 --> 00:15:04,677
凍りつくさなる純白の愛、
Pure white love like a frozen flower,

214
00:15:04,677 --> 00:15:06,377
雪のホロ！
Snowy holo!

215
00:15:06,377 --> 00:15:09,277
魔法少女ラミィ！
Magical Girl Lamy!

216
00:15:09,777 --> 00:15:10,977
ホロウィッチ！
holoWitches!

217
00:15:10,977 --> 00:15:13,277
フルキャスト！
Full Cast!

218
00:15:14,977 --> 00:15:15,977
行くよ！
Here I go!

219
00:15:16,977 --> 00:15:18,777
ほい、ほい、はい！
Hoi, hoi, hai!

220
00:15:27,477 --> 00:15:29,277
こん！
Kon!

221
00:15:34,477 --> 00:15:35,977
やめな。
Stop it.

222
00:15:36,777 --> 00:15:38,777
えい！
Ei!

223
00:16:02,577 --> 00:16:04,277
おいおいおい。
Whoa, whoa, whoa.

224
00:16:23,577 --> 00:16:26,777
ね、なんかこれ、まずくない？どんどん強くなってる。
Hey, isn't this getting bad? They're getting stronger.

225
00:16:26,877 --> 00:16:30,777
みんなが奴らを倒すより、不安と恐れが膨れ上がるほうが早いみたい！
The fear and anxiety are growing faster than you can defeat them!

226
00:16:30,977 --> 00:16:32,777
そんな！
No way!

227
00:16:34,077 --> 00:16:35,777
うちのせい...
It's my fault...

228
00:16:39,777 --> 00:16:43,777
...うちが、あんなもの怖いって思っちゃうせいで...
...because I keep thinking those things are scary...

229
00:16:44,277 --> 00:16:45,277
そんなこと...
That's not...

230
00:16:45,477 --> 00:16:47,077
わかってるの。
I know it.

231
00:16:47,177 --> 00:16:49,277
おかしいよね、あんなのが、
It's weird, isn't it? To be...

232
00:16:49,777 --> 00:16:52,577
こんな、どうしようもなく怖いなんて。
...this helplessly terrified of them.

233
00:16:53,777 --> 00:16:58,777
だから、今日も我慢して、頑張ろうって、思ったのに。
That's why I thought I'd just endure it and do my best today.

234
00:16:59,277 --> 00:17:03,277
でも... でもやっぱり！
But... But I just can't!

235
00:17:04,077 --> 00:17:06,277
おかしくなんてないよ。
It's not weird at all.

236
00:17:07,577 --> 00:17:08,777
カノンさん...
Kanon-san...

237
00:17:09,577 --> 00:17:12,777
誰にだって、苦手なものがある。
Everyone has something they're not good at.

238
00:17:12,877 --> 00:17:14,777
怖いもの。嫌いなもの。
Things they fear. Things they hate.

239
00:17:15,777 --> 00:17:19,777
人に何でそんなものが、って言われても、
Even if people ask why you're bothered by such things,

240
00:17:20,777 --> 00:17:24,277
どうしようもないことって、やっぱりあるよ。
there are just some things you can't help.

241
00:17:28,877 --> 00:17:30,277
そうだよ！
That's right!

242
00:17:30,377 --> 00:17:34,277
何が苦手とか、何が怖いかとかは関係なくて、
What you're bad at or what you fear doesn't matter.

243
00:17:34,377 --> 00:17:38,777
大事なのは、今、ミオちゃんが辛いって思ってるかどうかだから！
What matters is whether you're hurting right now, Mio-chan!

244
00:17:39,977 --> 00:17:41,777
遠慮しないで。
Don't hold back.

245
00:17:41,877 --> 00:17:45,777
頼ってほしいにぇ！
I want you to lean on us!

246
00:17:46,577 --> 00:17:48,777
だって、そういうのさ。
Because, you know,

247
00:17:48,877 --> 00:17:52,777
うちら、お互い様じゃん！
we're all in this together!

248
00:17:53,677 --> 00:17:58,277
誰かの辛さ、誰かの苦手は、他の誰かがカバーする。
When one of us hurts or struggles, the others cover for them.

249
00:17:58,377 --> 00:18:01,777
お互い、そうやって、やってきたんだから！
That's how we've always made it through!

250
00:18:01,777 --> 00:18:03,277
今だって！
Even now!

251
00:18:07,277 --> 00:18:09,277
こんなに頑張れる！
We can fight this hard!

252
00:18:12,577 --> 00:18:15,777
ホロウィッチ、コラプターは、
holoWitches, the Corruptors

253
00:18:15,877 --> 00:18:19,777
夢落ちした人の恐れと不安から生まれ、
are born from the fear and anxiety of the fallen,

254
00:18:19,877 --> 00:18:22,777
その心を深く沈ませてしまう。
sinking their hearts into the depths.

255
00:18:23,577 --> 00:18:26,277
夢落ちって、どうしてそれを...？
The fallen? How do you know about that...?

256
00:18:26,877 --> 00:18:29,777
でも、私は知ってる。
But I know this.

257
00:18:30,777 --> 00:18:33,277
君たちなら、ホロウィッチなら、
If it's you, if it's the holoWitches,

258
00:18:33,377 --> 00:18:37,277
辛い、苦しい、悲しい、きつい...
no matter how painful, agonizing, or sad it gets...

259
00:18:37,777 --> 00:18:44,777
そんな、自分一人の力じゃ抜け出せない暗闇の中にいても、
even in a darkness you can't escape alone,

260
00:18:46,777 --> 00:18:50,277
夢を、光を届けてくれる。
you will bring forth dreams and light.

261
00:18:51,777 --> 00:18:53,277
任せて！
Leave it to us!

262
00:18:59,377 --> 00:19:01,777
さあ、みんな。ホロウィッチが戦ってくれる。
Now, everyone. The holoWitches are fighting for us.

263
00:19:04,277 --> 00:19:07,277
では、私たちにできるのは？
So, what can we do?

264
00:19:08,277 --> 00:19:10,777
そう、私たちの声で、思いで、
That's right, with our voices and our feelings,

265
00:19:12,777 --> 00:19:16,277
彼女たちを応援することだ！
we must cheer them on!

266
00:19:17,777 --> 00:19:21,277
いざ、トリック・オア・トリート！
Now, Trick or Treat!

267
00:19:24,277 --> 00:19:26,277
仮装狂騒曲
Masquerade Rhapsody

268
00:19:26,277 --> 00:19:27,777
作詞：TOPHAMHAT-KYO (FAKE TYPE.)
Lyrics: TOPHAMHAT-KYO (FAKE TYPE.)

269
00:19:27,777 --> 00:19:29,277
作曲：FAKE TYPE.
Composition: FAKE TYPE.

270
00:19:29,877 --> 00:19:32,577
あれよという間に飲み込まれ
Swallowed up in the blink of an eye

271
00:19:32,777 --> 00:19:36,277
橙色のタイダルウェーブ やっこ やっこ
An orange tidal wave, heave-ho, heave-ho

272
00:19:36,677 --> 00:19:39,677
ハンドメイドからオーダーメイドまで仕掛ける大流行
From handmade to custom-made, starting a huge craze

273
00:19:39,877 --> 00:19:42,877
蜘蛛の巣から見せ物小屋まで纏めて大集合
From spider webs to sideshow tents, everyone gather 'round

274
00:19:43,077 --> 00:19:45,977
添えも添えたり不遇な世界に お揃いの装束で ヘケケケケ
Adding more to this unfortunate world in matching outfits, hee-hee-hee-hee

275
00:19:46,077 --> 00:19:49,277
これ見よがしの奴隷よ どおしようどれい？ 呪術的フォーメーションで ホップ ステップ トレイン
Look at these slaves, what to do, slaves? In a magical formation, hop step train

276
00:19:49,577 --> 00:19:50,877
メーデーが特急から
Mayday from the express train

277
00:19:50,977 --> 00:19:52,377
ジョニーをどつければ
If we wallop Johnny

278
00:19:52,477 --> 00:19:55,677
チヤホヤしたりされたりがいいでしょ？ 今更じゃ物足りない義務感も
Pampering and being pampered feels good, right? Obligation isn't enough anymore

279
00:19:55,777 --> 00:20:01,577
茶劇は一旦切って エブリバディ ご機嫌 エブリタイム センシティブ ティブ チグハグ お祭り騒ぎの 始まりだ
Cut the charade, everybody's happy, everytime sensitive-tive, the mismatched mayhem begins

280
00:20:00,792 --> 00:20:01,892
アニマで制御不能
Uncontrollable by the soul

281
00:20:01,992 --> 00:20:03,092
アッハッハー
Ah ha ha!

282
00:20:03,192 --> 00:20:05,692
Unbiased Igy- Igy viral
Unbiased Igy- Minimanimon

283
00:20:05,792 --> 00:20:08,792
恐ろしあそあそばせ
Pray, join this terrifying play

284
00:20:08,892 --> 00:20:11,792
ばかりあがりまわる月に針が落ちるわ
The needle falls on the moon as it rises and spins

285
00:20:11,892 --> 00:20:14,792
おちょぼ口で笑うカボチャたちと歌うわ
Singing with the pumpkins laughing with puckered lips

286
00:20:14,892 --> 00:20:17,992
それが合図 魔物たちが目覚め踊るわ
That is the signal; the monsters awaken and dance

287
00:20:18,092 --> 00:20:21,092
こうなればあとは思いのまま
Now that it's begun, everything is as we wish

288
00:20:23,092 --> 00:20:26,392
Hollow 骨抜きダンサボ
Hollow, the bone-chilling dance floor

289
00:20:26,692 --> 00:20:29,592
スケアクロウも跳び跳ねまわる
The scarecrows too are leaping around

290
00:20:29,792 --> 00:20:32,992
Hollow 月夜のタンテボ
Hollow, the moonlit turntable

291
00:20:33,192 --> 00:20:35,992
くるくるお静まり we gotta party night
Spinning round, quiet down, we gotta party night

292
00:20:40,892 --> 00:20:43,092
Anyway, enjoy the party night

293
00:20:43,692 --> 00:20:46,592
ワーワーワー 不気味なプルプル
ジャッケルクキジョ ムリムリ
Wah-wah-wah, eerie tremors
Jack-o'-lantern energy, no way, no way

294
00:20:46,792 --> 00:20:49,692
背徳に洗濯はジェスなしで
夜更けのヘラヘラゲラヘルヤ
Washing away immorality without a guess
Late-night smirking, laughing, Hallelujah

295
00:20:49,792 --> 00:20:52,792
What's my 素敵なナイト
見つからなくてもすでにバーナイト
What's my wonderful night?
Even if not found, it's already a bar night

296
00:20:52,992 --> 00:20:55,892
雰囲気貸切 着ぐるみ島で
から早出きるりぐる
Private atmosphere on Costume Island
Making a quick getaway, dressing up

297
00:20:56,792 --> 00:20:58,192
仮のショーも魂のホンモノならば魅了
Even a temporary show fascinates if the soul is real

298
00:20:58,292 --> 00:20:59,792
敷き待ちなる嬢 城一両
The lady waiting, the castle's worth

299
00:21:00,692 --> 00:21:02,692
サーサーサー最高に霧のリボン
Come, come, come, the ultimate misty ribbon

300
00:21:02,792 --> 00:21:05,892
ガラパゴスに交わる異世界大降臨パーティー
A grand descent party of another world in Galapagos

301
00:21:06,692 --> 00:21:09,092
振り切れる鼓動
The heartbeat racing past the limit

302
00:21:09,892 --> 00:21:12,692
悪目な魔女のドラキュラお酒を煽るわ
The wicked witch's Dracula quaffs the liquor

303
00:21:12,892 --> 00:21:15,892
寡黙そうなデュラハンも頭を振るわ
Even the silent-looking Dullahan shakes its head

304
00:21:16,092 --> 00:21:18,992
紳士的なミイラスらも服がはだけるわ
Even the gentlemanly mummies have their clothes disheveled

305
00:21:19,192 --> 00:21:22,392
ドあれば愉快全開のまま
With a bang, staying in full-blown delight

306
00:21:24,092 --> 00:21:27,292
本性あらわに暴れよ
Reveal your true nature and run wild

307
00:21:27,692 --> 00:21:30,392
その仮装も清楚になる
Even that costume becomes neat and clean

308
00:21:30,792 --> 00:21:33,992
狂騒曲のタンテボ
The turntable of rhapsody

309
00:21:34,192 --> 00:21:36,992
アイアイアイお静まり we gotta party night
Aye-aye-aye, quiet down, we gotta party night

310
00:21:37,992 --> 00:21:40,992
Hi-Fi All night All night 眠れやしない
Hi-Fi, all night, all night, can't sleep a wink

311
00:21:44,792 --> 00:21:47,892
Fly high All night All night 鳴りやまない
Fly high, all night, all night, the sound won't stop

312
00:21:49,792 --> 00:21:52,792
古代も空遊び
Even in ancient times, playing in the sky

313
00:21:52,992 --> 00:21:55,892
ランタンはまるで魂
The lanterns are just like souls

314
00:21:56,092 --> 00:21:59,092
以前奇怪なジャンボリー
As before, a strange jamboree

315
00:21:59,792 --> 00:22:02,692
闇冷えすハロウィン
A darkness-chilled Halloween

316
00:22:04,092 --> 00:22:07,392
Hollow 骨抜きダンサボ
Hollow, the bone-chilling dance floor

317
00:22:07,692 --> 00:22:10,592
スケアクロウも跳び跳ねまわる
The scarecrows too are leaping around

318
00:22:10,792 --> 00:22:13,892
Hollow 月夜のタンテボ
Hollow, the moonlit turntable

319
00:22:14,092 --> 00:22:17,092
くるくるお静まり we gotta party night
Spinning round, quiet down, we gotta party night

320
00:22:21,892 --> 00:22:24,092
Anyway, enjoy the party night

321
00:22:26,192 --> 00:22:29,092
くるくるお静まり we gotta party night
Spinning round, quiet down, we gotta party night

322
00:22:37,892 --> 00:22:39,692
ホロウィッチの力が乱れてる。
HoloWitch's power is in disarray.

323
00:22:39,792 --> 00:22:42,292
恐れと不安が解けていくんだ。
歌の力…
Fear and anxiety are melting away.
The power of song...

324
00:22:42,692 --> 00:22:45,892
みんなの声の力で！
With the power of everyone's voices!

325
00:22:46,592 --> 00:22:50,592
ホロウィッチのみんな、がんばれ！
いつも応援してるよ！
Go for it, everyone in HoloWitch!
I'm always rooting for you!

326
00:22:47,992 --> 00:22:49,692
みんな、のってるね！
Everyone's getting into it!

327
00:22:50,692 --> 00:22:54,592
ホロウィッチが力を合わせれば勝てない敵はいない！
頑張って！ホロウィッチ！
If HoloWitch joins forces, there's no enemy they can't beat!
Do your best! HoloWitch!

328
00:22:51,792 --> 00:22:55,192
おかげでこっちもやる気いっぱいなのな。
Thanks to that, I'm full of motivation too.

329
00:22:57,092 --> 00:23:00,892
さあ、行って。ホロウィッチ。
心を苛むトリックに…
Now, go, HoloWitch.
Against the tricks that torment the heart...

330
00:23:02,892 --> 00:23:04,992
とびっきりのトリートを！
A special treat!

331
00:23:12,892 --> 00:23:14,492
みんな、応援ありがとう。
Everyone, thanks for the support.

332
00:23:14,592 --> 00:23:17,392
