魔法を
Magic

535
00:40:09,911 --> 00:40:11,711
かけるよ
I'll cast

536
00:40:11,711 --> 00:40:14,611
We can stay oh yeah!

537
00:40:33,711 --> 00:40:37,111
最高のステージだったよ、ホロウィッチ。
That was an amazing stage, holoWitches.

538
00:40:37,411 --> 00:40:39,211
ほんと、ほんと！
Totally, totally!

539
00:40:39,211 --> 00:40:41,411
みんな、お疲れ様。
Good job, everyone.

540
00:40:41,711 --> 00:40:43,111
カノンさん、
Kanon-san,

541
00:40:43,111 --> 00:40:48,211
あの、今日は本当にありがとうございました。
um, thank you so much for today.

542
00:40:49,111 --> 00:40:54,011
それで、あなたはどうして、夢落ちとか僕たちのことを？
So, why do you know about Dreamfalls and us?

543
00:40:55,111 --> 00:40:57,511
私、前に夢落ちして
I fell into a Dreamfall before...

544
00:40:57,511 --> 00:41:00,811
君たちに助けられたことがあるんだ。
...and you girls saved me.

545
00:41:02,611 --> 00:41:03,911
ええーっ！？
What!?

546
00:41:04,011 --> 00:41:07,311
だから、あの時の自分と同じように
So, just like I was back then...

547
00:41:07,311 --> 00:41:13,611
夢落ちして苦しんでいる誰かを見ると、放っておけなくて。
...I can't just leave someone behind when I see them suffering from a Dreamfall.

548
00:41:14,411 --> 00:41:16,411
あと、実は...
Also, actually...

549
00:41:17,311 --> 00:41:21,211
今日このステージに出ることにしたのも
The reason I decided to appear on this stage today...

550
00:41:21,211 --> 00:41:24,811
君たちが出ると聞いたからなんだ。
...was because I heard you girls were going to be here.

551
00:41:24,811 --> 00:41:27,511
もう一度会えたらって思って。
I thought I might be able to see you again.

552
00:41:28,311 --> 00:41:31,611
だから今日は、えっと...
So today, um...

553
00:41:32,011 --> 00:41:34,211
すごく嬉しかった！
...I was very happy!

554
00:41:35,011 --> 00:41:37,611
これからも頑張ってね、ホロウィッチ。
Keep doing your best, holoWitches.

555
00:41:38,211 --> 00:41:39,611
そ、それじゃあ。
W-well then.

556
00:41:42,811 --> 00:41:46,011
また！ぜひまた！
See ya! For sure, see ya again!

557
00:41:52,611 --> 00:41:57,111
あの人自身が夢落ちしてホロウィッチに助けられていたから
Because he was saved by holoWitches when he fell into a Dreamfall himself...

558
00:41:58,211 --> 00:42:01,011
知っていたんだ。夢落ちした時の辛さも
...he knew. He knew the pain of falling into a Dreamfall...

559
00:42:01,011 --> 00:42:07,411
そんな時、誰かが手を差し伸べてくれることの嬉しさも。
...and the joy of someone reaching out their hand in a time like that.

560
00:42:08,311 --> 00:42:13,511
そっか。みこたちが少しでも誰かの力になれたら
I see. If we can be even a little bit of a source of strength for someone...

561
00:42:14,111 --> 00:42:18,911
その誰かが、また別の誰かの力になってくれるんだね。
...then that someone will, in turn, become a source of strength for someone else.

562
00:42:19,211 --> 00:42:21,911
そうだね。しかもさ、そんだけじゃなくて
Right. And it's not just that...

563
00:42:21,911 --> 00:42:25,311
うちらの力になってくれたりもするわけじゃん。
...they also become a source of strength for us, don't they?

564
00:42:25,711 --> 00:42:29,511
あの人や、今日応援してくれたみんなみたいに。
Like him, and everyone who supported us today.

565
00:42:29,911 --> 00:42:31,411
それって...
That's...

566
00:42:31,711 --> 00:42:33,211
それって...
That's...

567
00:42:33,511 --> 00:42:36,311
それってすっごく...
That's super...

568
00:42:36,511 --> 00:42:39,811
すっごくトリート！
...Super Treat!

569
00:43:10,311 --> 00:43:14,511
キラキラ 宝石みたいに輝いてる
Sparkling, shining like a gem

570
00:43:15,011 --> 00:43:21,211
夢の結晶 みんなの宝物
Crystals of dreams, everyone's treasure

571
00:43:21,311 --> 00:43:25,711
時々 見失っちゃうこともあるけど
Sometimes we might lose sight of it, but...

572
00:43:26,111 --> 00:43:31,311
あふれ出した 光が僕を呼ぶんだよ
...the overflowing light calls out to me

573
00:43:33,111 --> 00:43:36,211
絶対 大丈夫
You'll definitely be okay

574
00:43:36,211 --> 00:43:43,011
ただ まっすぐでいることも 楽じゃない日もあるよね
There are days when even just staying true to yourself isn't easy

575
00:43:44,311 --> 00:43:46,811
諦めも
Giving up...

576
00:43:47,111 --> 00:43:49,811
苦しみも
...and suffering...

577
00:43:49,811 --> 00:43:54,211
重ねていこう 心叩き 放とう
...let's let them pile up, and then let our hearts beat and release them

578
00:43:55,411 --> 00:43:58,311
夢を 歌おう
Let's sing our dreams

579
00:43:58,311 --> 00:44:01,111
魔法に乗せて
Riding on magic

580
00:44:01,311 --> 00:44:06,011
何度も 立ち上がる 君と一緒に進んでく
Standing up again and again, I'll keep moving forward with you

581
00:44:06,111 --> 00:44:10,411
夢は 夢は まだ終わらない
Our dreams, our dreams haven't ended yet

582
00:44:10,611 --> 00:44:16,411
未来を 取り戻そう
Let's take back the future

583
00:44:16,911 --> 00:44:19,211
何度だって
As many times as it takes

584
00:44:19,311 --> 00:44:21,911
笑って
...keep smiling...

585
00:44:21,911 --> 00:44:25,411
もう一歩 歩き始めよう
...and let's start taking another step forward

586
00:44:25,611 --> 00:44:28,311
ホロウィッチ
holoWitches

587
00:44:28,311 --> 00:44:31,311
夢の先へ
To what lies beyond the dream

588
00:45:00,952 --> 00:45:04,152
きらり光り出すんだよ
They will begin to sparkle and shine

589
00:45:04,352 --> 00:45:07,352
頑張ってみても
Even if you try your best

590
00:45:07,552 --> 00:45:10,952
上手くいかない日の方が
There are days when things don't go well

591
00:45:10,952 --> 00:45:14,752
多く感じちゃったりするよね
And it feels like there are many of them, right?

592
00:45:14,752 --> 00:45:20,185
さぁ 不安な悲しみも
Come now, don't hold onto

593
00:45:20,185 --> 00:45:25,685
抱えないで 一人じゃない
Your uneasy sadness, you're not alone

594
00:45:25,685 --> 00:45:30,985
希望の種を 明日に蒔いたら
If you sow the seeds of hope for tomorrow

595
00:45:30,985 --> 00:45:37,519
一番に輝く 綺麗な花が咲くよ
The most beautiful flower will bloom brilliantly

596
00:45:37,519 --> 00:45:43,552
夢を 歌を 魔法に乗せて
Carrying our dreams and songs on magic

597
00:45:43,552 --> 00:45:49,152
何度も立ち上がる君と一緒に進んでく
I'll keep moving forward with you, as you stand up again and again

598
00:45:49,152 --> 00:45:54,552
夢は 夢はまだ終わらない
The dream, the dream is not over yet

599
00:45:54,552 --> 00:45:59,952
未来を取り戻そう
Let's take back the future

600
00:46:00,152 --> 00:46:05,552
何度だって笑って
Smile as many times as it takes

601
00:46:05,552 --> 00:46:08,652
もう一歩歩き始めよう
And let's take another step forward

602
00:46:08,652 --> 00:46:11,952
ホロウィッチ！ Oh yeah! さぁ！
HoloWitch! Oh yeah! Come on!

603
00:46:11,952 --> 00:46:25,119
夢の先へ
Toward the future of our dreams

604
00:46:30,119 --> 00:49:26,619
ありがとうございました
Thank you very much

